column5: Hey guys new too parry sound here working for the next month can anyway tell me good fishing spots for rainbow trout
Can’t help you but is your company hiring???

The Rainbow numbers are nothing like they were 2 years ago. The 30,000 fish that escaped from the fish farm have been depleted by Mannnnny happy fisherman. You might catch one off the Salt dock . If you have a boat you can fish beyond 100 ft of the fish farm where some escapees and occasional naturals still hang out. But as I said locals and GTA day fishers are getting far fewer than before.
Was a fun place to fish with kids,then well,as per the norm,WWW ruined it along with the ignorant garbage leaving scum and those that disrespected others . Those that know,know to well .
